                             /       |      \
                           /         |        \
                         /           |          \
                       /             |            \
               Run Left        Climb Down/Crouch  Run Right
          + shift key =                           + shift key =
        careful step left                      careful step right


The joystick works the same way as above using the directions
8, E, or I = NORTH (UP); 9, R, or O = NORTHEAST (UP TO THE RIGHT);
6, F, or L = EAST (RIGHT); 5, D, or K = SOUTH (DOWN);
4, S, or J = WEST (LEFT); 7, W, or U = NORTHWEST (UP TO THE LEFT).





